## chart main Project Status Crux
```mermaid
flowchart LR
  bounty["Bounty: managed Instagram creator outreach"]
  api["GREEN API control plane MVP"]
  store["GREEN Durable local store + idempotency"]
  delivery["YELLOW Adapter contract only"]
  ops["YELLOW Sender health model only"]
  beads["YELLOW Beads planning active"]
  next["Next: proof pack + execution routing"]
  bounty --> api
  api --> store
  bounty --> delivery
  bounty --> ops
  delivery --> beads
  ops --> beads
  beads --> next
  class api green
  class store green
  class delivery yellow
  class ops yellow
  class beads yellow
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
  classDef red fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c53030,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a0505
```

## chart epic-gantt Epic Status
