## chart erd Data Model ERD
```mermaid
erDiagram
  CAMPAIGN ||--o{ TARGET : includes
  CAMPAIGN ||--o{ PROVIDER_EVENT : receives
  CAMPAIGN ||--o{ SUPPRESSION_RECORD : creates
  CAMPAIGN ||--o{ APPROVAL_WORKBENCH : reviewed_by
  SENDER_ACCOUNT ||--o{ TARGET : assigned_to
  TARGET ||--o{ PROVIDER_EVENT : changes_status
  TARGET ||--o{ OPERATOR_EVIDENCE : records
  CAMPAIGN {
    string id
    string campaign
    string status
    string message
    datetime createdAt
  }
  TARGET {
    string handle
    string status
    string sender
    datetime scheduledAt
  }
  SENDER_ACCOUNT {
    string id
    string status
    int dailyLimit
    string cooldownUntil
  }
  PROVIDER_EVENT {
    string eventId
    string event
    datetime receivedAt
  }
  SUPPRESSION_RECORD {
    string handle
    string campaignId
    string reason
  }
  APPROVAL_WORKBENCH {
    string id
    string campaignId
    string updatedAt
  }
  OPERATOR_EVIDENCE {
    string kind
    string actor
    datetime at
  }
```
